             were indicted for <rs id="t18220220-57-off307" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220220-57-off307" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220220-57-off307" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18220220-57-cd308" type="crimeDate">2nd of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220220-57-off307 t18220220-57-cd308"></join>, four sheets, value 1 l.; six table-cloths, value 1 l,; twelve towels, value 12 s.; three aprons, value 3 s.; and four handkerchiefs, value 4 s.; the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18220220-57-victim640" type="victimName">
                           Mary 
                           Hobson
