                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220220-57-victim640 t18220220-57-viclabel309"></join>; and one shawl, value 1 l.; one pair stays, value 4 s.; one gown, value 4 s.; and three shifts, value 12 s.; the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18220220-57-victim642" type="victimName">
